%section#services
  .l-light
    .l-constrained
      .m-section
        %h1.m-section__title Services

        .l-grid.l-grid--3-cols---MQtablet
          .l-grid__span
            = link_to 'information-design-agency.html', class: "m-panel m-panel--interactive" do
              .c-summary
                .m-panel__title
                  %h2.c-summary__title.c-summary__title--accent Information Design

                %figure
                  .c-summary__figure.c-summary__figure--circle
                    = ui_svg 'chart', false, alt: "A complex graph", id: "icon_chart", class: "c-summary__figure--circle__image"

                %p.c-summary__copy
                  Do you have lots of data that you're struggling to show in a way that makes sense?
                %p
                  %b We find effective ways to communicate your data in meaningful ways.
          
          .l-grid__span
            = link_to 'ui-design-agency.html', class: "m-panel m-panel--interactive" do
              .c-summary
                .m-panel__title
                  %h2.c-summary__title.c-summary__title--accent UI Design
                
                %figure
                  .c-summary__figure.c-summary__figure--circle
                    = ui_svg 'devices', false, alt: "A laptop, tablet and phone", id: "icon_devices", class: "c-summary__figure--circle__image"

                %p.c-summary__copy
                  Big or small, in your pocket or on your wall; we have the experience and skill to make the most of the display.
                %p
                  %b If it has a screen, we can design for it. 

          .l-grid__span
            = link_to 'front-end-development.html', class: "m-panel m-panel--interactive" do
              .c-summary
                .m-panel__title
                  %h2.c-summary__title.c-summary__title--accent Front End Development

                %figure
                  .c-summary__figure.c-summary__figure--circle
                    = ui_svg 'code', false, alt: "A command line terminal window", id: "icon_code", class: "c-summary__figure--circle__image"

                %p.c-summary__copy
                  We think about the code from that start. Often prototyping and testing interactions with users.
                %p
                  %b Code is optimised for performance across multiple devices.

        .m-section__footer
          = link_to "Get in touch", "contact.html", class: "o-button o-button--primary"